-- Guus Hiddink Signs 18-Month Contract to Coach Russia’s Anzhi Soccer Club
-- B y   P a u l   A b e l s k y
-- 2012-02-17T14:20:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-17/guus-hiddink-signs-18-month-contract-to-coach-russia-s-anzhi-soccer-club.html
Guus Hiddink, who took  Russia  to the
semifinals at soccer’s 2008 European Championship, was named as
coach of Russian club Anzhi Makhachkala after signing a 1 1/2
year contract today, according to a  statement  published on the
team’s website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Abelsky at 
 pabelsky@bloomberg.net  